original_title: Australia’s Flinders Uni. delegation visits Port City Commission
original_body_lines: A delegation from Flinders University and their local team met with the Chairman and top officials of the Port City Economic Commission for talks to expand its presence in Sri Lanka, and discuss several other areas of interest. Flinders University is a public research university based in Adelaide, South Australia, with a footprint extending across 11 locations in South Australia and the Northern Territory.
